                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>10 feet, @Check[will|dc:24]. Enemy creatures that enter or begin their turn in the area must attempt a Will save. Regardless of the result of the saving throw, the creature is then temporarily immune to the aura for 1 minute.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is frightened 1 and can't use reactions for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, and the creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} as it sobs uncontrollably.</p>"
                },
