                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The brigade draws or reloads their crossbows, then launches a ranged attack in the form of a volley. This volley is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 120 feet that deals @Damage[3d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:21|basic] save). When the troop is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
