                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The brigade slashes mercilessly at enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] (@Check[reflex|dc:21|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[1d8[piercing],1d4[spirit]|options:area-damage]{1d8 piercing damage plus 1d4 spirit}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[2d8[piercing],2d4[spirit]|options:area-damage]{2d8 piercing damage plus 2d4 spirit}</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(2d8+4)[piercing],2d4[spirit]|options:area-damage]{2d8+4 piercing damage plus 2d4 spirit}</p>"
                },
